========================================
recutils -- read and manipulate recfiles
========================================

The GNU recutils are a set of libraries and utilities supporting the
rec format: a human-readable, text-based format to store little medium
sized databases. These are the Python bindings for the librec library.

Check the GNU recutils project home page for the latest release,
mailing lists, etc.

* http://www.gnu.org/software/recutils

Installation
------------

To install this module type the following::

   python setup.py install

Dependencies
------------

This module requires the librec library, which may be obtained from:

* http://www.gnu.org/software/recutils

